name: Sanjay Metal
overview:
Established in the year 2012 we, “Sanjay Metal (India)”, are prominent stockists and suppliers as well as traders of a wide range of Stainless Steel Profiles and Non Ferrous Metals.

Products: Pipes & Tubes Industrial Flanges Buttweld Fittings Forged Fittings Metal Bolts Metal Nuts Non Ferrous Metals

Our Team: Ours is a team of dexterous professionals who have been the power hose of the company. With their great support we have been able to carry out all trade activities proficiently. Their sincerity towards work and dedication and hardworking attitude has helped us stay firm on quality and reputation.

Vendor Base: Being a coveted supplier and trader we have made stringent associations with some of the reputed vendors of market. They are the ones availing us with th superior quality products manufactured in complete tandem with the industrial standards. The vendors whom we collaborate with are one of the most reliable and reputed ones in the market.

Quality Assurance: Owing to our strict adherence to quality, we have been able to offer to our customers a comprehensive range of stainless steel products. Sourced from the most reliable vendors the offered range has been made by them as per the standards of the industry.

Customers Satisfaction: We are a client oriented firm and all our actions have been directed towards the satisfaction of the clients only. Our clients have been in consistent demand of the products we offer them with and have widely appreciated the quality of the same.
